message.body: How ya doing baby?
Good good :) How are you, my love?
Good. I'm catching up on Fridays micro lecture.
Boo.
Ah. Gross. Hope it doesnt stink too badly. Glad youre getting that outta the way tho
Me too. Now there's less to do tomorrow....yay! But I'm miss you!!!!!!!!!
Mmmhm! But i know. It stinks. Felt like we barely saw each other
I know. It was bittersweet.
5 Days and we do it again :)
Yay!!! More bitter sweetness! And then the following week!
Haha yea!! And then big one!! :)
Yes yes yes!!! They're predicting snow Tuesday into Wednesday. If they do...that'd be pretty nice. Cause they're saying 5-8 inches. Of course that will probably change to less than an inch. Boo
Haha no no. Have hope!
Well I was wrong. It's 5-8 tomorrow night into Tuesday...so maybe there's hope! Otherwise...I give up any chance of having a snow day!
Itll happen! You gotta get at least one
I hope so!!! Hehe. Going to bed now. Good night my love. Get home safe!
Went from 5-8 to 3-6 inches. Boo.
What the heck! I leave and you get all the snow! I love you!
Its not snowing at all!
It will be. You're supposed to be get 5-10 inches baby.
Haha lucky me :-p You wanna come back and shnuggle eh eh?
Yes yes and yes!!!!!
Haha come on come on come on!! I'll be home in half hr, meet ya there!
Hahah. Let me go hop on a bus before the snow gets here!
Ahah yesh! I like that plan!
Haha. IN YO DREAMS FOOL! Go to bed. Dream of me on your bed. Last night I dreamt that I was riding a child's tricycle. Needless to say...I stopped riding it after a while. Haha.
Haha thats...thats a confusing dream. I dont quite understand the plot, the conflict...or the resolution. So imma go to bed. I love you, so so very much :)
I love you too! Goodnight!
Have a good day!
So sorry baby!!! I was eating/cleaning up after dinner.
Are you at work already???
In the metro, my love. 3+ Inches of snow already :)
I hate you! I tried to call! I'm sorry I missed you!
